<item>
            <title>[SPR-966] PropertyResourceConfigurer.convertPropertyValue never gets called</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-966</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;API docs say that you can override convertPropertyValue(String) in subclasses of PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer to perform custom value conversions like decrypting an encrypted value.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately, convertPropertyValue (or, more specifically, convertProperties) never gets called by Spring. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="11595">SPR-966</key>
            <summary>PropertyResourceConfigurer.convertPropertyValue never gets called</summary>
